@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Courier
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title envShare - System Architecture

actor Developer
actor Admin

node "Developer Workstation" {
  component "CLI (esai)\nNode.js + Commander" as CLI
}

cloud "Internet / LAN" as Net

node "Edge" {
  component "Caddy\nTLS Termination\nReverse Proxy" as Caddy
}

node "Application Network" {
  component "Backend API\nExpress + Prisma" as API
}

database "PostgreSQL 16\nEncrypted secrets at rest" as DB

Developer --> CLI : push/pull/run/set
Admin --> CLI : project and member administration

CLI --> Net
Net --> Caddy : HTTPS requests
Caddy --> API : /api/*
API --> DB : SQL queries

note left of CLI
CLI-only operation
No web dashboard
end note

note right of API
Security controls:
- Helmet headers
- CORS allowlist
- Rate limiting
- JWT + refresh tokens
- Audit logging
end note

note right of DB
Core entities:
- users
- projects
- environments
- secrets
- user_secret_values
- secret_versions
- audit_logs
end note

@enduml
